# Evidence signing keys, signatures, and bundles — never commit private key
# material or signed evidence. `evidence keygen` writes these, and the docs steer
# report/evidence output into ./out; keep all of it out of version control.
*.key
*.pub
*.pem
*.p8
*.sig.json
*.evidence.zip
/out/

